<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8391621>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Eucalantica nestori n. sp. (A–C, F) and E. polita (D–E). A. Holotype (male) in dorsal view; B. Paratype (male, IRG-001) in lateral view; C. Male genitalia (paratype, IRG-001) in ventral view; D. Male genital capsule in ventral view (after Sohn & Nishida 2011); E. Phallus (after Sohn & Nishida 2011); F. Female genitalia and abdominal segments VIII–IX (paratype, SJC-1377). Scale bars = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8391621/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

